The paper focuses on visual exploration and analysis of data, which is a common topic in the Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC) sub-category. The paper also discusses the challenge of selecting and transforming data for visualization, which is a common topic in the Database (cs.DB) sub-category. The recommendation system developed in the paper uses natural language processing techniques, which is a common topic in the Information Retrieval (cs.IR) sub-category. The paper also discusses the effectiveness of visualizations, which is a common topic in the Visualization (cs.VIS) sub-category. Finally, the paper discusses the parsing of visual-exploration sequences, which is a common topic in the Natural Language Processing (cs.CL) sub-category.
